Effective 9/1/82 (Daylight Saving Time). Schedules are subject to change without notice.
NOTES:
1. Please note extraordinarily convenient departure
times from both New York and Miami. Especially
good for business people making connections
from Chicago and Washington. And note, too: we
are the only airline with non-stop 747 service
between Miami and Buenos Aires.
2. Remember that Lima departure from Los Angeles.
Direct. And it's the best departure time of any
airline.
3. All flights are 747s. With marvelous service.
Sleeper seats in First Class. Free wine and music
in all classes.
4. Important: Free New York Helicopter service from
Manhattan, Newark/LaGuardia airports to JFK for
First-Class/All Year Economy passengers.
5. Up to 15% commissions. Now that's a nice note,
isn't it?
